    <section>
        <title>Recommended Reading</title>
        
        <para>If you are new to eXist, we recommend to at least scan through the following 
            documents to get an overview of the most important features:</para>
        
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para><ulink url="quickstart.xml">Quick Start</ulink></para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><ulink url="xquery.xml">XQuery</ulink></para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><ulink url="devguide_xquery.xml">Writing Web Applications using XQuery</ulink></para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><ulink url="tuning.xml">Performance Tuning</ulink></para>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
        
        <para>Also, there are some <ulink url="articles">articles, tutorials and blog posts</ulink>
            which may provide valuable information.</para>
    </section>
      
